title: BRIEF-I3D gets 597,000 zloty net order from college in Prague
text:
BRIEF-I3D gets 597,000 zloty net order from college in Prague Sept 3 
Sept 3 I3D SA : 
* Gets a 597,000 zloty ($158,427) net order for the implementation of software and application of driving simulator for a college in Prague, the Czech Republic Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: ($1 = 3.7683 zlotys) (Gdynia Newsroom) Trending On Reuters
